sqs_message = lambda_input[ "Records" ][0][ "body" ]

import boto3
import json
import time

def main( lambda_input, context ):
    sqs_message = lambda_input[ "Records" ][0][ "body" ]
    s3 = boto3.resource(
        "s3"
    )
    object = s3.Object(
        "lambdatestbucketpewpew",
        str( int( time.time() ) ),
    )
    object.put(
        Body=sqs_message
    )
    return sqs_message
